data.description: Welcome! You have finally found the perfect location to enjoy the peaceful small town living that you have been looking for with an easy commute to Denver via I-70. This like 2020 house will immediately make you feel at home with the open floor plan, huge lot with no direct neighbor behind.  The back yard is an open palette for your landscaping dreams.  As you enter the home you are greeted by  living room and open kitchen and dining area. The kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and a window overlooking the backyard. The master bedroom with ensuite full bath and walk in closet. There are 2 additional secondary bedrooms and  full bathroom all in the ranch/one story floor plan.  The unfinished basement is a full foot print, has rough in plumbing for a bathroom and ready for you to utilize as you wish. 2 car garage. Access to the Deer Trail School is just a few short blocks, perfect distance to walk to school or the library. Don't miss this opportunity to own an affordable home located in this quaint small town.  Security System/Cameras included, Buyer can activate service through ADT. $50/ month. Seller has Solar Panel Lease.  $130/month.  Average utility Bills are $25-$30/month.  Lease to be transferred to Buyer at Closing or Buyer can purchase.  Open House Saturday 9/2. 12-2pm.  Showings Start Saturday 9/2 at 11am. All offers due by Monday at 5pm with acceptance deadline of Tuesday at 5pmSeller to offer 1% Buy Down for 1 year with Preferred Lender.
